title: Beautiful  property!  Will Consider Rental Debt Over 3 years!
posting_body: Located off of Highway 121 at Independence Parkway w/ beautiful golf course views.

Interiors include plank flooring, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ceramic surface cook tops, built-in bookcases, tray ceilings, crown molding, lighted ceiling fans, decorative fireplaces, and washer/dryer.

Spectacular amenities include resort-style pool and fountains, pavilion w/picnic tables and BBQ, indoor basketball and racquetball, fitness center, sand VB, playground, backyards, game room and business center.
Covered parking and direct-access garages are available, as is WiFi in the clubhouse, business center and poolside.
Please call Desiree with Dash Realty
